# ViralBoost AI – Website Systems, Kaise Kaam Karta Hai, aur Fayde (Full Detail)

Is file mein website ke saare systems, unka kaam karne ka tareeka, aur users ko kis cheez se kya fayda hota hai – sab detail mein diya gaya hai.

---

## 1. WEBSITE KYA HAI AUR KISKE LIYE HAI

**ViralBoost AI** ek SaaS platform hai jisse content creators, YouTubers, aur agencies apne videos ka viral potential analyze kar sakte hain. Ye website:

- Video analysis (YouTube, Facebook, Instagram, TikTok, direct upload) karti hai
- Viral score, title suggestions, hashtags, best posting time deti hai
- Trends, competitor analysis, analytics dashboard provide karti hai
- Free, Pro ($2.5/month), aur Enterprise ($5/month) plans ke through access milta hai

**Fayda:** Creators ko data-driven decisions lene mein help; time bachta hai aur content strategy improve hoti hai.

---

## 2. LOGIN AUR AUTHENTICATION SYSTEM

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Do tarah se login:** (1) **Unique ID (6 digit) + PIN** – jaldi login ke liye (2) **Email + Password** – full account access
- Signup par email verify OTP bhejta hai; OTP verify hone ke baad user banta hai
- Password **Forgot Password** se reset ho sakta hai (link email par aata hai)
- JWT token se session maintain hota hai; sidebar se **Logout** kar sakte hain

### APIs
- `POST /api/auth/login` – Email + password login
- `POST /api/auth/login-pin` – Unique ID + PIN login
- `POST /api/auth/register` – Naya user
- `POST /api/auth/send-otp` – OTP bhejna
- `POST /api/auth/verify-otp` – OTP verify
- `GET /api/auth/me` – Current user details (role, plan, expiry, account manager, etc.)
- `POST /api/auth/password-reset` – Reset link request
- `PUT /api/auth/password-reset` – Naya password set (token ke sath)

### Fayde
- Secure login; PIN se fast access; password reset se account recover; har user ko apna 6-digit ID milta hai.

---

## 3. PLAN AUR ROLE SYSTEM

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Free** → role: **user** | **Pro** → role: **manager** | **Enterprise** → role: **admin**
- **Super-admin** role plan se change nahi hota (manual set)
- Login ya payment verify hone par role plan ke hisaab se set ho jata hai
- Sidebar aur profile mein **Plan** aur **Expires: X days left** dikhta hai

### Fayde
- Plan ke hisaab se sahi access; Pro/Enterprise ko zyada features; expiry clear dikhti hai.

---

## 4. VIDEO ANALYSIS SYSTEM

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- User video **URL** de sakta hai (YouTube, Facebook, Instagram, TikTok) ya **file upload** kar sakta hai
- Har video par: **hook analysis** (shuruat attract karti hai?), **thumbnail analysis**, **title analysis**, **viral prediction**, **hashtags**, **trending score**, **best posting time** nikala jata hai
- **Title optimization:** Free = 3 suggestions, Pro/Enterprise = 10 suggestions
- **Hashtag generator:** 10–20 hashtags (plan ke hisaab)
- Result **Viral Optimizer** page par dikhta hai; copy kar sakte ho
- Analysis DB mein save hota hai; **My Videos** se list dekhi ja sakti hai

### APIs
- `POST /api/videos/youtube` – YouTube URL analyze
- `POST /api/videos/facebook` – Facebook URL
- `POST /api/videos/instagram` – Instagram URL
- `POST /api/videos/tiktok` – TikTok URL
- `POST /api/videos/upload` – File upload analyze
- `POST /api/videos/bulk-analyze` – Ek saath multiple URLs (Pro/Enterprise, max 10)

### Fayde
- Har video ke liye viral score, better titles, hashtags, posting time – content zyada engage kare; bulk se time bachta hai.

---

## 5. VIRAL PREDICTION AUR AI

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- Hook, thumbnail, title, trending score, duration se **viral probability** (0–100) aur **confidence** nikalti hai
- Rule-based + optional **TensorFlow.js ML model** (viral dataset se train)
- Enterprise users **Custom AI model training** trigger kar sakte hain: `POST /api/ai/train` (zyada data se model improve)

### Fayde
- Creators ko pata chal jata hai video kitna viral ho sakta hai; improve kahan karna hai ye bhi suggestions se samajh aata hai.

---

## 6. TRENDING AUR REAL-TIME TREND ANALYSIS

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Trending** page: hashtag/keyword trends, growth velocity, opportunity score
- **Discover trends** API se rising/peak/declining trends milte hain
- Hashtag generator trending topics use karta hai taaki suggestions relevant rahein

### APIs
- `GET /api/trends/discover` – Trends list
- `GET /api/trending` – Trending topics

### Fayde
- Trending topics use karke content zyada discover ho sakta hai; hashtags up-to-date rehte hain.

---

## 7. BEST POSTING TIME PREDICTIONS

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Posting Time** page par platform (YouTube, Facebook, Instagram, TikTok) ke hisaab se **heatmap** (day × hour) aur **best day + hour** dikhta hai
- Category (comedy, education, music, etc.) ke hisaab se time adjust ho sakta hai

### APIs
- `GET /api/posting-time` – Heatmap + best time

### Fayde
- Sahi time post karke views aur engagement badhane mein madad.

---

## 8. COMPETITOR ANALYSIS

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- Competitor channel ID daalne par unke successful patterns (titles, hashtags, video length, posting times) analyze hote hain
- **Channel Audit** / **Facebook Audit** pages par multiple videos analyze karke insights milte hain
- Competitor limit plan ke hisaab se: Free = 3, Pro = 50, Enterprise = unlimited

### APIs
- `POST /api/competitor/analyze` – Competitor insights
- `GET /api/channel/videos` – Channel se video list (RSS/API)

### Fayde
- Competitors se seekh kar apna content strategy improve kiya ja sakta hai.

---

## 9. ANALYTICS DASHBOARD

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Analytics** page: total videos, total analyses, average viral score, engagement rate
- Top performing videos, growth, retention, heatmap, benchmark APIs se data aata hai
- **Export:** CSV / Excel / PDF (white-label option: company name + logo URL se branded report)

### APIs
- `GET /api/analytics/overview`
- `GET /api/analytics/growth`, `/api/analytics/retention`, `/api/analytics/heatmap`, `/api/analytics/benchmark`
- `GET /api/export/analytics?format=pdf|csv|excel` – Report download

### Fayde
- Performance ek jagah; reports share karne/white-label se branding strong hoti hai.

---

## 10. CONTENT CALENDAR AUR SCHEDULING

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Content Calendar** page par din aur platform ke hisaab se posts plan kiye ja sakte hain
- Schedule APIs se calendar data aur post schedule manage hota hai

### APIs
- `GET /api/schedule/calendar`
- `POST /api/schedule/post`

### Fayde
- Planning se consistent posting; content calendar se discipline badhti hai.

---

## 11. SUBSCRIPTION AUR PAYMENT

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Pricing** page: Free / Pro ($2.5/month) / Enterprise ($5/month); **Subscribe** se Razorpay checkout
- Payment verify hone par plan activate; **role** plan ke hisaab set (Pro→manager, Enterprise→admin)
- **Subscription** page: current plan, usage (analyses, storage), **Payment History**; har entry se **PDF receipt** download
- Receipt currency user/invoice ke hisaab (e.g. Rs-4,500 INR)

### APIs
- `POST /api/payments/create-order` – Razorpay order
- `POST /api/payments/verify-payment` – Verify + activate plan + set role + send receipt email
- `GET /api/subscriptions/usage` – Usage stats
- `GET /api/subscriptions/invoices` – Invoices (plan, amount, currency, date)

### Fayde
- Safe payment; clear plan/usage/receipts; PDF se record rakhna easy.

---

## 12. SUPPORT SYSTEM (EMAIL / 24/7 PRIORITY)

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Support** page: subject + message se ticket create; list of tickets dikhti hai
- Plan ke hisaab priority: Free = normal, Pro = high, Enterprise = priority (24/7)
- Admin baad mein reply kar sakta hai (reply field DB mein)

### APIs
- `GET /api/support` – My tickets
- `POST /api/support` – Create ticket

### Fayde
- Har plan user ko support milta hai; Enterprise ko priority; issues track ho jate hain.

---

## 13. TEAM COLLABORATION (ENTERPRISE)

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- Enterprise user **team** bana sakta hai (max 10 members)
- Owner **invite link** generate karta hai; doosre users link se **join** karte hain
- Team list: `GET /api/team`; create: `POST /api/team`; join: `POST /api/team/join` (token)

### Fayde
- Agencies/teams ek hi plan ke under collaborate kar sakte hain.

---

## 14. WHITE-LABEL REPORTS

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- User **Settings** se **Company name** aur **Logo URL** set karta hai
- Analytics **export** (PDF/HTML report) par ye branding use hoti hai – report apne brand ke saath dikhta hai

### Fayde
- Reports client ko apne brand ke saath de sakte ho; professional look.

---

## 15. API ACCESS (PUBLIC API)

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Settings** se user **API key** create karta hai (vb_xxx…); key sirf ek baar dikhai deti hai
- Kisi bhi request mein header: **X-API-Key: your_key**
- **Public endpoint:** `GET /api/public/v1/usage` – usage + subscription (API key se auth)

### APIs
- `GET /api/settings/api-keys` – List keys
- `POST /api/settings/api-keys` – Create key
- `DELETE /api/settings/api-keys?id=...` – Delete key
- `GET /api/public/v1/usage` – Usage (X-API-Key)

### Fayde
- Apne tools/apps se usage aur plan check kar sakte ho; automation possible.

---

## 16. CUSTOM INTEGRATIONS (WEBHOOKS)

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Settings** mein **Webhook URL** save karte ho
- Jab bhi koi video **analysis complete** hoti hai, tumhari URL par **POST** request jati hai – event name + payload (videoId, title, viralProbability, platform, etc.)

### APIs
- `GET /api/settings/webhook` – Current webhook
- `POST /api/settings/webhook` – Save URL

### Fayde
- External systems (CRM, Slack, custom dashboard) ko real-time event mil sakte hain; integrations easy.

---

## 17. PRIORITY PROCESSING

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- Pro/Enterprise users ke analyses DB mein **priority: 'high'** ke sath save hote hain
- Future mein agar queue-based processing aayi to inko pehle process kiya ja sakta hai

### Fayde
- Pro/Enterprise ko better response time / priority milega jab queue implement ho.

---

## 18. DEDICATED ACCOUNT MANAGER (ENTERPRISE)

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- Super-admin kisi Enterprise user ke liye **account manager email** set karta hai (admin panel: user → Set account manager)
- Ye email **Settings** aur **/api/auth/me** mein dikhta hai – “Contact: manager@company.com”

### Fayde
- Enterprise users ko direct contact; personalized support.

---

## 19. SUPER ADMIN PANEL

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Super-admin** role wale user `/dashboard/super` par jaate hain
- **Users:** list, create user, modify (name, role), reset password, set/clear PIN, delete user
- **Send plan receipts:** saare paid users (Pro/Enterprise) ko unke current plan ka receipt email
- **Notify all users:** subject + message se sabko notification email
- **Database Tables:** collections select karke data grid, search, pagination
- Sidebar: Dashboard, My Videos, Viral Optimizer, Channel Audit, Facebook Audit, Trending, Hashtags, Posting Time, Analytics, Content Calendar, Pricing, Subscription, etc.

### APIs
- `GET/POST /api/admin/users`
- `PATCH/DELETE /api/admin/users/[id]` (set-role, reset-password, set-pin, set-account-manager, update, etc.)
- `POST /api/admin/send-plan-receipts`
- `POST /api/admin/notifications/send`
- `GET /api/admin/data/collections`
- `GET /api/admin/data/collections/[name]` (pagination, search)

### Fayde
- Pura user management, notifications, receipts, aur data ek jagah se control.

---

## 20. USER PROFILE AUR SETTINGS

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Profile:** name, bio, profile picture, social links, preferences (notifications, email updates, dark mode)
- **Settings** page: Account manager (read-only), White-label (company name, logo URL), API keys, Webhook URL
- **Subscription** page: plan, usage, payment history, PDF download

### APIs
- `GET /api/user/profile` – Profile
- `PUT /api/user/profile` – Update (name, bio, white-label, webhook, etc.)
- `GET /api/user/usage` – Usage + limits

### Fayde
- Sab kuch ek jagah; branding, API, webhook control; usage clear.

