## 23. OVERALL FAYDE (SUMMARY)

1. **Creators:** Viral score, titles, hashtags, posting time se content better banata hai; time bachta hai.
2. **Agencies/Teams:** Enterprise se team collaboration, white-label, account manager – clients ko branded reports aur dedicated support.
3. **Data-driven decisions:** Trends, competitor analysis, analytics se strategy clear hoti hai.
4. **Automation:** API + webhooks se apne tools se integrate karke workflows automate ho sakte hain.
5. **Support:** Ticket system se har plan user ko help; Enterprise ko priority.
6. **Admin:** Super admin se users, notifications, receipts, DB sab control; plan ke hisaab role automatically set.

