## 24. MISSING YA INCOMPLETE FUNCTIONS / SYSTEMS (KAM KYA BAAKI HAI)

Website mein kuch features abhi puri tarah se kaam nahi kar rahe hain ya incomplete hain, jinhe future mein fix ya build karna padega:

1. **SmartGuru AI / LMS (Learning Management System)**:
   - Notes, Video progress, aur Kurs (Course) ke data models (`models/` folder mein) currently missing hain. LMS ka part partially build hua hai.
2. **AI Support System**:
   - Support tickets kaam karte hain, lekin OpenAI/AI ke auto-reply (Super Admin toggle for AI support) wala feature abhi "planning" aur partial configuration phase mein hai.
3. **Facebook Page Videos Auto-Fetching**:
   - `/api/facebook/page/videos` API abhi sirf ek khali array `[]` return karti hai. Facebook Graph API ke restrictions aur Meta App review ki wajah se ye feature direct fetching support nahi kar raha.
4. **Custom AI Model Training (Enterprise)**:
   - `POST /api/ai/train` endpoint claim karta hai ki ye AI train karta hai, lekin backend mein koi actual TensorFlow.js pipeline ya GPU heavy training script connected nahi hai (ye sirf ek mock/placeholder hai).
5. **Real Background Job Queue (Priority Processing)**:
   - Database mein "priority: high" save hota hai, par server par **Redis ya RabbitMQ** jaisa koi real Background Queue worker chal nahi raha hai.
6. **Instagram & TikTok Direct Uploads**:
   - YouTube OAuth aur YouTube par direct video upload karna properly ban chuka hai, par Instagram API aur TikTok API ke through direct video posting functionality abhi properly integrated nahi hai.

